      • loadColorFromJSON

        public Color loadColorFromJSON(org.json.simple.JSONArray jsonArray)
        Loads a Color from a JSON array. The array is loaded as [red, green, blue] or a [red, green, blue, alpha]. Any values after alpha are ignored.
        Parameters:
        jsonArray - The array of color values.
        Returns:
        The Color or null if the jsonArray is null.
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - If the array contains fewer than three values.
